Sum:

- rabbitmq concepts: publish, exchanges, queues, subscrib
- rabbitmq management, add vhost and user, list exchanges and queues
- simple pubsub with default exchange
- fancy pubsub with direct-based, topic-based exchange

Details:

1.a) rabbitmq concepts
http://www.rabbitmq.com/tutorials/amqp-concepts.html
amqp: advanced messaging queue protocol

1.b) rabbitmq management commands
http://www.rabbitmq.com/man/rabbitmqctl.1.man.html
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_connections -p vhost
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_exchanges -p vhost
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_queues -p vhost
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_bindings -p vhost
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_users -p vhost
$ sudo rabbitmqctl list_vhosts -p vhost

2.a) simple pubsub with default exchange
http://www.cloudamqp.com/docs/nodejs.html

2.b) a pubsub with direct-based or topic-based exchange
https://github.com/postwait/node-amqp

